   :from_source: F

   [50 pts] Write to program to read 3 non-negative integers as input from the user and sort them in an ascending order.  

   You are not allowed to use a system sort function or a data structure like a list in this problem.

   Example run of the program:

   ::

     Please enter the first non-negative integer: 15
     Please enter the second non-negative integer: 2
     Please enter the third non-negative integer: 91
     The sorted values are: 2 15 91

   ~~~~
   # Write your code here

   ====